name: JULIETTE'S WINTER
description:
By Grete Hjorth-Johansen [TW @ghjstudio_uk].
Animated sequence of light painted digital photographs.
35sec @ 3240x2160px 30fps MP4. Edition of 50.

JULIETTE'S WINTER:
With a crystal clear mind, Juliette contemplates her ambitions for the future. Cold and alone, yet she needs no one.

JULIETTE SERIES:
In this series we encounter the many faces and moods of the beautiful and mysterious girl from Uncanny Valley. Juliette—is she real? Is she a dream? The many different views of her face explore notions like love, passion, death and fear.

See the series: https://ghjstudio.com/series/juliette-series/
